name: LOG_LEVEL
description:
The output log level of the SDK.Since
  v3.3.0

parameters.LOG_LEVEL_NONE: 0: Do not output any log information.

parameters.LOG_LEVEL_INFO:
0x0001: (Default) Output FATAL, ERROR,
                        WARN, and INFO level log information. We
                        recommend setting your log filter as this level.

parameters.LOG_LEVEL_WARN:
0x0002: Output FATAL, ERROR, and WARN level
                        log information.

parameters.LOG_LEVEL_ERROR: 0x0004: Output FATAL and ERROR level log information.
